1
00:00:49,620 --> 00:00:53,820
=Camellias=

2
00:00:53,860 --> 00:00:56,740
=Episode 11=

3
00:00:57,200 --> 00:00:58,759
General Rong,

4
00:00:58,759 --> 00:01:00,039
his love for you...

5
00:01:02,799 --> 00:01:05,079
I'm afraid it wasn't brotherly love.

6
00:01:06,959 --> 00:01:08,239
What did you say?

7
00:01:08,239 --> 00:01:09,599
I said

8
00:01:10,920 --> 00:01:12,760
if Rong Xiu's love for you

9
00:01:12,760 --> 00:01:14,560
wasn't brotherly love at all...

10
00:01:17,959 --> 00:01:19,680
Consort Rong,

11
00:01:20,359 --> 00:01:22,079
being so clever,

12
00:01:22,239 --> 00:01:23,959
surely you must know

13
00:01:23,959 --> 00:01:25,640
that the General kept a woman

14
00:01:25,640 --> 00:01:28,239
at his manor who looked
so much like you.

15
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:30,799
He painted her brows for her daily,

16
00:01:31,319 --> 00:01:32,799
held her on his lap.

17
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:35,959
Those aren't things a brother

18
00:01:36,799 --> 00:01:39,040
would do to his sister.

19
00:01:40,319 --> 00:01:42,640
Perhaps there's another possibility.

20
00:01:45,560 --> 00:01:47,879
Before you became Consort Rong,

21
00:01:48,239 --> 00:01:50,159
you already had something with him.

22
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:53,359
Later, you put an end to it.

23
00:01:53,760 --> 00:01:55,000
That day,

24
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:57,239
when I tricked Rong Xiu
into pinning you down,

25
00:01:57,239 --> 00:01:58,760
you killed him so His Majesty

26
00:01:58,760 --> 00:02:00,359
- wouldn't see it.
- Shut your mouth!

27
00:02:00,599 --> 00:02:02,280
How dare you slander me!

28
00:02:02,280 --> 00:02:03,840
Slander or not,

29
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:06,799
you know the truth.

30
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:10,560
Rong Zhaohua,

31
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:12,960
you killed your own brother
to secure His Majesty's love,

32
00:02:13,360 --> 00:02:15,680
to become Consort Rong,

33
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:18,240
for that supreme power.

34
00:02:19,639 --> 00:02:21,599
How ruthless you are.

35
00:02:21,599 --> 00:02:22,439
Do you think I can't

36
00:02:22,439 --> 00:02:23,919
kill you right now?

37
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:32,560
I can kill you,

38
00:02:32,840 --> 00:02:34,719
but why rush?

39
00:02:35,759 --> 00:02:38,360
I haven't had my fill of watching you

40
00:02:38,719 --> 00:02:40,759
look so helpless.

41
00:02:55,759 --> 00:02:57,360
(I can't die.)

42
00:02:57,840 --> 00:02:59,919
(I can't die here.)

43
00:03:04,759 --> 00:03:06,919
(How can you achieve anything
if you're this impulsive?)

44
00:03:08,199 --> 00:03:10,120
(Take this as a lesson.)

45
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:12,520
(In this world, only calmness)

46
00:03:12,520 --> 00:03:13,800
(and composure bring success.)

47
00:03:23,080 --> 00:03:24,240
(Perhaps)

48
00:03:24,719 --> 00:03:26,240
(that's what he was thinking.)

49
00:03:31,759 --> 00:03:34,159
(I must survive.)

50
00:03:48,599 --> 00:03:49,840
Father.

51
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:52,719
I have finally brought you

52
00:03:52,719 --> 00:03:54,000
the body of our enemy.

53
00:04:02,439 --> 00:04:03,080
My Lord,

54
00:04:04,039 --> 00:04:05,680
I have served you for years.

55
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:07,159
To see your vengeance fulfilled today,

56
00:04:07,159 --> 00:04:08,400
it is my honor.

57
00:04:18,120 --> 00:04:19,279
My Lord.

58
00:04:20,879 --> 00:04:22,680
Are you worried about the Holy Maiden?

59
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:26,480
Did the Holy Maiden

60
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:28,199
really kill General Rong Xiu?

61
00:04:28,519 --> 00:04:29,160
Impossible.

62
00:04:31,319 --> 00:04:32,079
Killing Rong Xiu

63
00:04:32,079 --> 00:04:34,319
does nothing for her revenge.

64
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:38,920
Even if she's impulsive,

65
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:40,759
she wouldn't kill without reason.

66
00:04:41,199 --> 00:04:42,839
But His Majesty gave me

67
00:04:42,839 --> 00:04:44,720
Rong Xiu's body to bury the matter.

68
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:47,920
As for what really happened,

69
00:04:49,879 --> 00:04:51,319
it doesn't matter.

70
00:04:53,279 --> 00:04:55,160
This matter is over.

71
00:04:55,399 --> 00:04:56,560
Then, My Lord,

72
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:58,439
you're really abandoning her?

73
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:09,920
Useless.

74
00:05:10,600 --> 00:05:13,120
Just as I thought, not my match.

75
00:05:14,879 --> 00:05:17,120
My sister has been gone so long,

76
00:05:17,639 --> 00:05:18,839
yet you still can't let go

77
00:05:18,839 --> 00:05:20,920
of your hatred for her.

78
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:22,879
Surely His Majesty

79
00:05:22,879 --> 00:05:24,759
hasn't forgotten her either.

80
00:05:24,759 --> 00:05:25,560
Shut up!

81
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:27,160
Your sister

82
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:28,360
was nothing but a trinket

83
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:31,079
the Zhao Tribe sent to curry favor.

84
00:05:31,079 --> 00:05:33,519
She dared to try to take my love.

85
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:35,199
She deserved to die.

86
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:37,920
And you deserve the same.

87
00:05:46,399 --> 00:05:47,360
You actually...

88
00:05:47,360 --> 00:05:48,800
Isn't this what you taught me?

89
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:50,079
To challenge you.

90
00:05:50,279 --> 00:05:51,600
Consort Rong.

91
00:05:52,800 --> 00:05:54,000
Kill me,

92
00:05:54,360 --> 00:05:55,720
and you won't live either.

93
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:57,639
My life doesn't matter.

94
00:05:58,240 --> 00:06:00,160
I just want you dead.

95
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:08,000
Your sister,

96
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:10,360
in the end, Zhu Yunqi

97
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:12,600
tortured her to death
in the Palace of Punishment.

98
00:06:12,879 --> 00:06:14,079
If you die,

99
00:06:14,079 --> 00:06:16,639
who will kill Zhu Yunqi?

100
00:06:16,639 --> 00:06:19,759
Who will avenge your sister?

101
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:21,519
Zhu Yunqi

102
00:06:21,519 --> 00:06:23,399
is cold-hearted,

103
00:06:23,399 --> 00:06:25,279
cruel, and volatile.

104
00:06:25,279 --> 00:06:26,120
He is

105
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:28,240
the one who truly

106
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:29,720
killed your sister.

107
00:06:33,879 --> 00:06:34,639
Guards!

108
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:43,120
How foolish.

109
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:46,439
You still believe me?

110
00:06:46,439 --> 00:06:48,920
Do you really think
you'll leave here alive?

111
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:50,199
Go tell His Majesty

112
00:06:51,079 --> 00:06:52,600
I've had my fun with her.

113
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:54,439
Kill her.

114
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:20,759
What is this?

115
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:22,120
These are the records

116
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:23,920
of General Rong Xiu's corruption
over the years.

117
00:07:23,920 --> 00:07:24,959
Consort Rong, you should

118
00:07:24,959 --> 00:07:26,360
know Rong Xiu best.

119
00:07:26,639 --> 00:07:27,480
Surely you don't think

120
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:28,720
he took Minister Shen's family

121
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:30,079
just for military supplies?

122
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:34,920
I'm curious,

123
00:07:36,279 --> 00:07:38,480
if this reached His Majesty,

124
00:07:39,639 --> 00:07:41,759
how do you think he would deal with you?

125
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:44,759
My brother is dead.

126
00:07:44,759 --> 00:07:45,959
Do you think I care

127
00:07:45,959 --> 00:07:47,480
about any of this now?

128
00:07:47,480 --> 00:07:49,959
Your family's honor and your favor
with His Majesty

129
00:07:49,959 --> 00:07:51,639
are inseparable.

130
00:07:52,519 --> 00:07:54,319
If you truly didn't care,

131
00:07:54,319 --> 00:07:55,959
why would you have killed
your own brother

132
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:58,120
to save yourself?

133
00:07:58,759 --> 00:08:00,079
Nonsense!

134
00:08:00,439 --> 00:08:01,800
How dare you slander me!

135
00:08:01,800 --> 00:08:02,399
True

136
00:08:02,759 --> 00:08:03,560
or false,

137
00:08:03,839 --> 00:08:04,560
does it matter?

138
00:08:08,959 --> 00:08:11,040
It seems you truly don't care.

139
00:08:14,439 --> 00:08:15,759
Then I was overthinking.

140
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:21,639
Wait.

141
00:08:26,439 --> 00:08:28,600
Jiang Yukui is still
in the Mirror Prison.

142
00:08:28,839 --> 00:08:30,279
But you're too late.

143
00:08:30,480 --> 00:08:32,720
Last night, I handed her over
to His Majesty.

144
00:08:33,279 --> 00:08:34,960
She'll be beheaded at dawn tomorrow.

145
00:08:36,360 --> 00:08:37,279
But tonight,

146
00:08:37,279 --> 00:08:38,879
she's still in the Mirror Prison.

147
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:40,320
I can

148
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:42,440
do you a small favor.

149
00:08:43,519 --> 00:08:44,639
I can help you

150
00:08:45,039 --> 00:08:45,840
swap her out.

151
00:08:51,039 --> 00:08:52,879
Tonight, His Majesty will come
to my chambers.

152
00:08:53,559 --> 00:08:55,480
I'll also call the guards away
from the Mirror Prison.

153
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:57,039
Before dawn

154
00:08:57,559 --> 00:08:59,399
will be your best window.

155
00:09:00,759 --> 00:09:01,799
After tonight,

156
00:09:02,440 --> 00:09:03,960
Jiang Yukui will be dead.

157
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:06,080
From then on, you can take her
wherever you want.

158
00:09:06,559 --> 00:09:07,639
Anywhere.

159
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:27,720
Yukui.

160
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:44,840
Leave us.

161
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:49,120
Where is she?

162
00:09:49,879 --> 00:09:52,399
The Holy Maiden was
in the Mirror Prison.

163
00:09:52,399 --> 00:09:54,120
Could His Majesty have grown impatient

164
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:55,600
and had her executed early?

165
00:09:58,679 --> 00:09:59,679
I asked you.

166
00:09:59,679 --> 00:10:00,519
Where is she?

167
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:02,840
You can't blame me for this.

168
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:05,039
But if you kill me now,

169
00:10:05,039 --> 00:10:06,600
you won't find her,

170
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:08,360
and you'll alert the enemy.

171
00:10:08,360 --> 00:10:09,559
Not worth it.

172
00:10:10,360 --> 00:10:11,399
Perhaps

173
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:13,279
you should let me go.

174
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:14,679
Maybe

175
00:10:14,679 --> 00:10:16,080
I can still be of use.

176
00:10:22,600 --> 00:10:24,440
(Why was I brought here?)

177
00:10:25,240 --> 00:10:26,480
(There's no Mirror Prison here.)

178
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:27,960
(Isn't she afraid)

179
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:29,480
(I can use the Divine Power now?)

180
00:10:48,679 --> 00:10:49,799
It seems

181
00:10:50,679 --> 00:10:52,559
you truly aren't afraid.

182
00:10:53,320 --> 00:10:55,639
(A rare opportunity.)

183
00:10:58,159 --> 00:11:00,159
I know you can't bear to lose me.

184
00:11:00,159 --> 00:11:01,200
Why should I be afraid?

185
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:05,240
Then let's see

186
00:11:05,440 --> 00:11:06,799
what kind of surprise

187
00:11:08,120 --> 00:11:09,840
you can give me.

188
00:11:28,240 --> 00:11:29,799
(Now is when he's)

189
00:11:30,279 --> 00:11:31,879
(least guarded.)

190
00:11:40,279 --> 00:11:41,919
The Seventh Prince.

191
00:11:42,720 --> 00:11:45,320
You're so tender.

192
00:11:46,639 --> 00:11:47,919
Since childhood,

193
00:11:47,919 --> 00:11:50,639
you've been bathed in goat's milk.

194
00:11:51,879 --> 00:11:53,039
No wonder

195
00:11:54,080 --> 00:11:55,320
your skin

196
00:11:55,919 --> 00:11:57,320
feels so smooth.

197
00:11:57,320 --> 00:11:58,279
Get away!

198
00:11:59,080 --> 00:12:00,039
Don't hit me!

199
00:12:00,879 --> 00:12:02,440
Your mother

200
00:12:03,840 --> 00:12:06,480
was banished to the forsaken palace.

201
00:12:06,759 --> 00:12:09,600
She couldn't endure the torment.

202
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:13,480
To survive in this palace,

203
00:12:14,440 --> 00:12:17,320
she had to rely on me.

204
00:12:18,039 --> 00:12:19,159
So

205
00:12:19,399 --> 00:12:20,639
she gave you

206
00:12:20,879 --> 00:12:23,039
to me.

207
00:12:23,679 --> 00:12:24,559
(So from a young age,)

208
00:12:24,559 --> 00:12:26,320
(he had no mother to protect him.)

209
00:12:35,720 --> 00:12:37,360
Where is Your Majesty going?

210
00:12:37,360 --> 00:12:38,639
Don't forget,

211
00:12:39,600 --> 00:12:40,840
the you of today

212
00:12:41,120 --> 00:12:42,759
is no longer the you of the past.

213
00:12:43,480 --> 00:12:45,720
You are strong enough now,

214
00:12:46,240 --> 00:12:48,840
strong enough to face those
who have hurt you.

215
00:12:49,440 --> 00:12:50,639
Go, Your Majesty.

216
00:12:51,799 --> 00:12:54,159
None of what you see is real.

217
00:12:55,759 --> 00:12:57,679
Go conquer your inner demons.

218
00:13:15,940 --> 00:13:17,340
♪The moon sinks in the west♪

219
00:13:17,820 --> 00:13:19,260
♪The cold lamp burns low♪

220
00:13:19,460 --> 00:13:22,580
♪No one knocks upon
the mountain gate♪

221
00:13:22,900 --> 00:13:26,700
♪Snow-white winds and moonlight
touch me first♪

222
00:13:29,660 --> 00:13:31,380
♪Pear blossoms fill the courtyard♪

223
00:13:31,380 --> 00:13:32,900
♪Yet love and hate entwine♪

224
00:13:33,260 --> 00:13:36,660
♪Bound by precepts,
yet craving worldly desires♪

225
00:13:36,660 --> 00:13:40,660
♪Gathering red beans
for half a lifetime♪

226
00:13:41,820 --> 00:13:44,980
♪The Buddha speaks of countless paths♪

227
00:13:44,980 --> 00:13:48,540
♪How can one glance spanning ages
save a wandering soul♪

228
00:13:48,540 --> 00:13:50,860
♪Trapped within
the space between your brows♪

229
00:13:50,860 --> 00:13:55,060
♪Falling deeper and deeper♪

230
00:13:55,500 --> 00:13:57,140
♪The green lamp sheds no light♪

231
00:13:57,140 --> 00:13:58,660
♪Upon one who entered the path♪

232
00:13:58,660 --> 00:14:01,860
♪The six senses cannot cleanse
the dust of the past♪

233
00:14:02,260 --> 00:14:04,180
♪In dreams, it's you♪

234
00:14:04,180 --> 00:14:05,580
♪Beyond dreams, no one♪

235
00:14:05,580 --> 00:14:08,900
♪Clinging to one obsession,
adrift in a sea of suffering♪

236
00:14:08,900 --> 00:14:12,300
♪I can't forget
the stars in your eyes♪

237
00:14:12,300 --> 00:14:15,860
♪Our fate had already taken root♪

238
00:14:15,860 --> 00:14:19,100
♪In this mortal world,
there is only us♪

239
00:14:19,100 --> 00:14:22,540
♪Hopelessly bound by love♪
